<div class="main-cause-holder">
	<div class="row main-cause-blocks">
		<div class="col-xs-8 col-xs-offset-2 concept">
			<h1> The concept </h1>

			The aim of ISIS is to create an Islamic state across Sunni areas of Iraq and in Syria. ISIS is violently conquering countries due to the ideology of creating so-called "Islamic State." The idea of this app is to satirize the fact that it is ridiculous and cruel to brutally murder thousands of innocent civilians to take over territory.
			</br>
			</br>
			This idea can also be applied to something more deep and resonating rather than satirizing. For example, if you conquer a state, we can create an emotional story of what brutality was needed in order to conquer it (e.g. your best friend dying, maybe even a automatically generated video displaying the brutality of conquering that country). Then you can relate it back to ISIS. Thereâ€™s a bunch of way you can go about this idea!
			</br>
			</br>
			P.S. Only California works. This app is just proof of concept :).
		</div>
	</div>

	<div class="row main-cause-blocks" id="dv-block1">
		<div class="block1-content">
			<div class="eluci-info-holder col-xs-12"> 
				<span class="maincause-sub-header">Choose your state to counquer</span>
				<div class="col-xs-3">
					<%= image_tag "california.png", class: "state" %>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>

	<div class="main-cause-blocks" id="dv-block2"
		data-bottom-top="top: 0px;"
		data-top="opacity: 1; top: -80px;"
		data-top-bottom="opacity: 0; top: -100px;">
		<h1 class="main-cause-headers-of-blocks-small"
			data-anchor-target="#dv-block2"
			data-bottom-top="opacity: 0.25; top: 0px"
			data-center-top="opacity: 1; top: 15px;">Choose you state to conquer</h1>

		<div class="row whatis-desc-holder">
			<div class="dv-whatis-desc col-xs-12 col-lg-3"
				data-anchor-target="#dv-block2"
				data-bottom-top="opacity: 0;"
				data-center-top="opacity: 1;">
				<div class="col-xs-12">
					<%= image_tag('california.png', class: 'state') %>
					<span class="whatis-desc-header">California</span>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="dv-whatis-desc col-xs-12 col-lg-3"
				data-anchor-target="#dv-block2"
				data-bottom-top="opacity: 0;"
				data-center-top="opacity: 1;">
				<div class="col-xs-12">
					<%= image_tag('florida.png', class: 'state') %>
					<span class="whatis-desc-header">Florida</span>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="dv-whatis-desc col-xs-12 col-lg-3"
				data-anchor-target="#dv-block2"
				data-bottom-top="opacity: 0;"
				data-center-top="opacity: 1;">
				<div class="col-xs-12">
					<%= image_tag('georgia.png', class: 'state') %>
					<span class="whatis-desc-header">Georgia</span>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="dv-whatis-desc col-xs-12 col-lg-3"
				data-anchor-target="#dv-block2"
				data-bottom-top="opacity: 0;"
				data-center-top="opacity: 1;">
				<div class="col-xs-12">
					<%= image_tag('texas.png', class: 'state') %>
					<span class="whatis-desc-header">Texas</span>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>




	<div class="main-cause-blocks" id="dv-block2">
		<div class="in-touch">
			<h1 class="main-cause-headers-of-blocks-small"
				data-anchor-target="#dv-block2"
				data-bottom-top="opacity: 0.25; top: 0px"
				data-center-top="opacity: 1; top: 15px;">See what the ideology was to counquer</h1>
		</div>
		<div class="row email-form-holder">
			<div class="dv-whatis-desc col-xs-offset-3 col-xs-6"
				data-anchor-target="#dv-block2"
				data-bottom-top="opacity: 0; left: 0px;"
				data-center-top="opacity: 1; left: 20px;">
				<div class="col-xs-12">
					<!-- <span class="whatis-desc-header">Domestic Violence</span> -->
					<!-- We won't spam you :). We'll only send you one email when we launch! -->
					<%= form_for @email, url: { action: 'create', controller: "emails" }, html: { class: 'email-form' }, remote: true do |f| %>
						<div class='input-group'>
							<%= f.text_field :email, placeholder: 'Enter why you want the state', class: 'form-control email-input' %>
							<div class="input-group-btn">
								<%= f.submit "Go!",  class: 'btn btn-default email-btn' %>
			  			</div>
			  		</div>
					<% end %>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>

		<div class="row footer">
			<div class="dv-whatis-desc col-xs-offset-3 col-xs-6 answer">
				
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</div>